info.description:
Synapsify’s REST API is based on a core set of linguistic algorithms, utilizing phonemics, natural language processing (NLP), machine learning, etc. The API has been designed to be as flexible as possible, and can be adapted to a very wide range of domains and fields of interest, including:

Reading any type of written content based on several dimensions;
Revealing the quality, balance, credibility and quotablity of such content and its most important topics and phrases;
Indexing and matching against other written content or customized indexes;
Enhancing the ability to discover, understand and segment actionable insights.
